sub_title: Passion for (Celtic) Languages & Cultures | Teacher & Academic | Organizational Talent | Goal-Getter |
summary:
I believe in worldwide connections between people through languages and cultures, and they have always been my passion. It is my goal to spread that passion as much as possible, either by teaching/educating, doing research, writing or any other way, so that everyone can feel included and ultimately the world will become an even more beautiful place. 

My specialties are Celtic and Germanic languages, literatures and cultures; academic research, writing, editing, translation, teaching, project co-ordination, management, quality assessment and international communication.

You can contact me through InMail.
